



Dear Sir
New York 21st May 1758



Yours of the 27th Apr. I Received as I did Sometime before yours of the 6th Inclosing one for Mr Richard Washington.1 which Letter I forwarded by mutilated Hampshire Man War she Saild the 3d Instant mutilated Sandy Hook with Lord Loudoun on Board mutilated no News but what is in the Inclosed paper Except that some of our Rangers & Indians have brought in about 20 french prisoner & 8 or 10 Scalps Lately but what Accots they give I dont know. I am Dear Sir Yr Afft. H. Sert

Bev: Robinson

